                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The neutrons were produced with a yield of",
                "approximately 3 to 4E10 n/(4pis). The deuteron ion",
                "beam current was 180 uA with of an energy of 250 keV.",
                "The solid tritium-titanium (T-Ti) target used in the",
                "generator was approximately 2.59 mg/cm2 thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
